{"tid":716598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"竹聯幫頭目遭三煞擄走毆斃","createTime":"2018-06-25T11:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T12:01:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c32803dac32457c3a4d766bafc9edafe80cc13c4","tid":716598,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:39:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180625/20430892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430892&d=j%2Fmkz3xy8RAYDM2hWATdMUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=12317a3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430892&h=f72e93ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180625/20430892</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月25日 <br />\n<br />\n竹聯幫頭目遭三煞擄走毆斃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180625/large/a1505a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180625%2Flarge%2Fa1505a.gif&h=f7c99caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方拘捕殺害陳智強（小圖）的疑兇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台北市又發生殺人棄屍案！竹聯幫南堂南賢會副會長、綽號「歹強」的陳智強（35歲），前日上午11時49分到南港區興中路停車場取車時，遭3人押走，自此失蹤。陳的友人擔心報案，警方展開追查。但案情一度陷入膠着，直到同日晚11時許，3名有幫派背景的男子在律師陪同下投案，聲稱數月前與陳的車輛相撞，雙方衝突才埋下殺機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兇徒自首稱撞車報復<br />\n<br />\n涉案的3名疑兇分別是李灝（25歲）、李志豪（25歲）及陳柏安（25歲），均異口同聲表示，他們把陳智強押走，以木棒、鐵棍將他活活打死。但警方認為案情不單純，懷疑3人行兇動機說法。警方經調閱監視器畫面，發現陳男遭3人套上黑色塑膠袋，隨後押上另一輛車，載到新北市鶯歌區三鶯路某荒廢的鐵皮倉庫，以預藏的鐵條、木棍將他活活打死。<br />\n<br />\n3人供出藏屍地點，警方派人到場發現陳智強被打得遍體鱗傷，頭部及四肢等傷痕纍纍，頭顱被打破、鮮血直流、早已無呼吸心跳。警方其後依涉嫌殺人罪，將3人移送新北地檢署偵辦。死者陳智強8年前曾因組織犯罪遭刑事局逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n周杰倫演唱會再助警捉逃犯<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n叫阿媽浸「84消毒液」去腳氣　腳趾GG發黑要切"},{"pid":"bab998eae1c339bd304945c948b8fc01bbed0c5a","tid":716598,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"又會自己認頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b193e51385c8e47b75bfd97748301a8b2aecd04","tid":716598,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab998eae1c339bd304945c948b8fc01bbed0c5a","tid":716598,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"又會自己認頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"替死鬼"},{"pid":"860b4ca75b127fb85a5834bdf689d04e33516f94","tid":716598,"uid":74128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"我們跟你們三..三聯幫關係幾好的"},{"pid":"8ad26ae3f6e46889b6ab31a0a912199e3e1526b5","tid":716598,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:01:16.000Z","msg":"咁愛支那，抵撚死"}]}